Nike Ready, Set 2-Piece Crew Set

$55.00

Made of organic cotton rib knit stretch fabric that feels gentle and soft on babies’ sensitive skin, this 2-piece set is all about comfort little athletes can play freely in. The crew top has a roomy cut and dropped shoulders for a relaxed fit and the matching pants have a stretchy waistband for a comfy feel and the tapered legs provide a fit that little ones can move easily in. The cuffs on both the crew and the pants are extra long and feature a contrast back so they can be folded and add versatile styling. Ready, set, GO!
